    <a title="Josephine (Jo)" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/5918846-josephine-jo"><img alt="Josephine (Jo)" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1500813731p2/5918846.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/337570689?book_show_action=true">May 27, 2012</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Josephine (Jo)" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Josephine (Jo)" href="/user/show/5918846-josephine-jo">Josephine (Jo)</a>
